snippet.title: Johnny Depp Warns that Amber Heard is DANGEROUS!
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp Warns that Amber Heard is DANGEROUS!
Under the heading Gone Potty, the Sun published the now-famous editorial written by tabloid executive editor Dan Wooten in April 2018. Wooten attacked Jk Rowling's choice to keep Johnny in the film in his column, accusing the author of being blinded by his acquaintance with the actor.
